com.ibm.team.process.common

Interface ISimpleMap


  • public interface ISimpleMap
    A simple mapping provides access to the set of keys and to the value stored for a given key.
    Since:
    0.5

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.Object get(java.lang.Object key)
      Returns the value stored in this map under the given key.
      java.util.Set keySet()
      Returns the set of keys.

    • Method Detail

      • keySet

        java.util.Set keySet()
        Returns the set of keys. There is no guarantee that this set updates when the simple map is modified.
        Returns:
        the set of keys, never null

      • get

        java.lang.Object get(java.lang.Object key)
        Returns the value stored in this map under the given key. Returns null if no value is stored for the given key.
        Parameters:
        key - the key
        Returns:
        the value for the given key or null
